txt.en: 'Talk to me to become \qKindred\q with the Men of the Sutcrofts.'
'\qKindred\q with the Men of the Sutcrofts, coming right up! Brush up on your agriculture lingo and you'll do just fine!'
Unless you are a part of the local 4H group (which I doubt you are), they probably don't know you. Don't worry, we'll fix that.
